items.name: AlphaHorizon-kernel
items.description: AlphaHorizon Kernel is a custom 64-bit Unix-like operating system kernel written from scratch in C and x86-64 Assembly. It features basic process management, memory handling, interrupt support, drivers, a simple shell, and filesystem components, designed for learning low-level OS development.
